---
// src/pages/14-scroll-animation.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro' // Sesuaikan path layout lo

// Simpan kodingan produksi universal ke string agar siap disalin
const codeSnippet = `<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.data('scrollReveal', () => ({
      revealed: false,
      init() {
        // Mendeteksi Intersection Observer berdasarkan viewport window global
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              this.revealed = true;
              observer.unobserve(entry.target); // Stop pantau jika sudah mekar sekali (performa optimal)
            }
          });
        }, {
          threshold: 0.15 // Aktif saat 15% area elemen masuk ke layar
        });
        observer.observe(this.$el);
      }
    }));
  });
</script>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-12">

  <div
    x-data="scrollReveal"
    :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-10'"
    class="transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl"
  >
    <div class="text-amber-400 text-lg mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i></div>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Fade Up Smooth</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Sangat ideal untuk mementaskan elemen grid layout, baris teks artikel, atau kartu pricing secara elegan.</p>
  </div>

  <div
    x-data="scrollReveal"
    :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-x-0' : 'opacity-0 -translate-x-16'"
    class="transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl"
  >
    <div class="text-sky-400 text-lg mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket"></i></div>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Slide From Left</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Cocok untuk menonjolkan visual gambar di sisi kiri atau daftar list poin fitur utama produk.</p>
  </div>

  <div
    x-data="scrollReveal"
    :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-x-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-x-16'"
    class="transform transition-all duration-700 ease-out p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl"
  >
    <div class="text-purple-400 text-lg mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left-to-bracket"></i></div>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Slide From Right</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Digunakan bersamaan dengan efek kiri sebagai penyeimbang ritme arah gerak visual mata pembaca.</p>
  </div>

  <div
    x-data="scrollReveal"
    :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 scale-100' : 'opacity-0 scale-90'"
    class="transform transition-all duration-500 cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl"
  >
    <div class="text-emerald-400 text-lg mb-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i></div>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Scale Bounce Pop</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Efek mekar memantul yang sangat mencuri perhatian. Sempurna dipasang pada tombol aksi CTA utama atau lencana diskon.</p>
  </div>

</div>`
---

<Layout title="14. Scroll Entrance Animation - Blueprint UI">
  <main
    class="mx-auto max-w-4xl bg-slate-950 px-4 py-12 font-sans text-slate-100"
  >
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-6">
      <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span
          class="rounded-md border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-amber-400"
          >14. MENENGAH</span
        >
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          Scroll Entrance Animation
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
        Paket animasi deteksi gulir halaman (*scroll entrance reveal*) ultra
        ringan memanfaatkan <code class="font-mono text-amber-400"
          >IntersectionObserver</code
        > dengan konfigurasi target root spesifik.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="preview-title">
      <h2
        id="preview-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Live Preview (Scroll di Dalam Boks Ini, Bro!)
      </h2>

      <div
        id="sandboxScrollContainer"
        class="h-96 overflow-y-auto scroll-smooth rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-inner"
      >
        <div
          class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 py-4 text-center"
        >
          <p class="animate-pulse text-xs text-slate-500">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down mr-1"></i> Scroll ke bawah di dalam kotak
            ini untuk memicu animasi...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-40"></div>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl space-y-6 pb-12">
          <div
            x-data="scrollRevealLocal"
            :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-10'"
            class="flex transform items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          >
            <div
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 text-sm text-amber-400"
            >
              <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">
                Efek 01: Fade Up Smooth
              </h4>
              <p class="mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-slate-400">
                Mekar mulus bergeser naik tipis saat tersentuh sensor gulir.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            x-data="scrollRevealLocal"
            :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-x-0' : 'opacity-0 -translate-x-16'"
            class="flex transform items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
            x-cloak
          >
            <div
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-sky-500/30 bg-sky-500/10 text-sm text-sky-400"
            >
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">
                Efek 02: Slide From Left
              </h4>
              <p class="mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-slate-400">
                Muncul meluncur dari sisi kiri area frame kontainer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            x-data="scrollRevealLocal"
            :class="revealed ? 'opacity-100 translate-x-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-x-16'"
            class="flex transform items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
            x-cloak
          >
            <div
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/10 text-sm text-purple-400"
            >
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left-to-bracket"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">
                Efek 03: Slide From Right
              </h4>
              <p class="mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-slate-400">
                Sisi penyeimbang kanan, meluncur presisi masuk ke tengah.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-900 pt-4 text-center">
          <button
            onclick="document.getElementById('sandboxScrollContainer').scrollTop = 0; setTimeout(() => window.location.reload(), 300);"
            class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/60 bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-300 transition-all hover:bg-slate-700 active:scale-95"
          >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right mr-1"></i> Gulir ke Atas & Reset Sensor
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="code-title">
      <h2
        id="code-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Clean Code (Production Ready)
      </h2>
      <article x-data="codeCopier" class="group relative">
        <button
          @click="copy()"
          :class="copied ? 'bg-emerald-500/20 border-emerald-500/40 text-emerald-400' : 'bg-slate-950/60 border-slate-800 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900'"
          class="absolute top-3 right-3 z-10 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95"
        >
          <i x-show="!copied" class="fa-regular fa-copy text-sm"></i>
          <i
            x-show="copied"
            class="fa-solid fa-check text-sm text-emerald-400"
            x-cloak></i>
          <span x-text="copied ? 'Copied!' : 'Copy'"></span>
        </button>
        <pre
          class="h-100 overflow-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 pr-20 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-300"><code>{codeSnippet}</code></pre>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="doc-title">
      <h2
        id="doc-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Dokumentasi Logika
      </h2>
      <article
        class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/50 p-5 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-400 md:text-sm"
      >
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200"
            >1. Alur Kerja Intersection Observer:</strong
          > Daripada memantau event gulir jendela global (<code
            class="font-mono text-slate-300"
            >window.addEventListener('scroll')</code
          >) yang boros konsumsi CPU karena berjalan ratusan kali per detik,
          kita menugaskan browser mendeteksi koordinat lewat objek pengamat
          internal. Logika <code class="font-mono text-yellow-400"
            >observer.unobserve(entry.target)</code
          > menyetop pemantauan seketika setelah transisi dipicu agar performa *frame
          rate* website lo tetep stabil **60fps** tanpa patah-patah.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200"
            >2. Manipulasi Kelas Transisi Tailwind:</strong
          > Modul ini mengandalkan kombinasi transisi utility CSS. Pola kodenya dijaga
          lewat binding reaktif <code class="font-mono text-slate-300"
            >:class="revealed ? 'opacity-100' : 'opacity-0'"</code
          >. Pengamanan kode teks bebas dari error compiler berkat pemakaian
          entitas HTML terisolasi.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-900 pt-6">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 transition-colors hover:text-white"
      >
        ← Kembali ke Dashboard Sandbox
      </a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.data('scrollRevealLocal', () => ({
      revealed: false,
      init() {
        const containerNode = document.getElementById('sandboxScrollContainer')

        const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
          (entries) => {
            entries.forEach((entry) => {
              if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                this.revealed = true
                observer.unobserve(entry.target)
              }
            })
          },
          {
            root: containerNode, // KUNCI UTAMA: Sensor membaca scroll boks ini, bukan window!
            threshold: 0.1,
          },
        )

        observer.observe(this.$el)
      },
    }))
  })
</script>

<script define:vars={{ codeSnippet }}>
  document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.data('codeCopier', () => ({
      copied: false,
      codeText: codeSnippet,
      copy() {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.codeText)
        this.copied = true
        setTimeout(() => {
          this.copied = false
        }, 2000)
      },
    }))
  })
</script>
